AI</span></a></i><i>, where he works directly with companies navigating these transitions.</i></p></td></tr><tr class=\"btn_row\"><td valign=\"top\" style=\"padding-bottom:45px;padding-left:45px;padding-right:45px;padding-top:45px;text-align:center;width:100%;word-break:break-word;\" class=\"dd\"><table width=\"100%\" role=\"none\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"margin:14px auto 14px auto;\"><tr><td align=\"center\" valign=\"middle\"><table role=\"none\" border=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\"><tr><td style=\"background-color:#d92656;border-radius:10px;mso-padding-alt:45px 14px;\" class=\"btn\"><a href=\"https://link.mail.beehiiv.com/v1/c/gz8SWVJceb6cjgT20MBnj%2F3XW0UvgdkBKEinHbDoB8R%2FCbIit6Sa%2F7mRtwsq%0AdhKff3tJ705uZ7Qpkx9Lrrsn7gLUZR86b4klGJbNqGwNUMq7xkxo6peIFaAg%0Ae41YEKrTVKRvztBVbUcR6yDqs82HNbn%2FNLjoTXa58SkZQ5as3bBsihkpD%2Bz2%0Ae1bdbNLh1QewZBGzw1imnBg%2Bm%2FYpIfE%2BNQ%3D%3D%0A/f59508ab8a2aa366\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer nofollow\" style=\"background-color:#d92656;border-radius:10px;color:#FFFFFF;display:inline-block;font-family:'Space Grotesk',Helvetica,Arial,sans-serif;font-size:16px;font-weight:normal;line-height:18px;padding:45px 14px;text-decoration:none;\"> Book a consultation </a></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr></table></td></tr><tr><td class=\"e\" align=\"left\" valign=\"top\" style=\"padding:45px 45px 5px;\"><h3 style=\"\">How did you like it?</h3></td></tr><tr><td class=\"ee e \" style=\"padding:0px 45px 45px;\"><div style=\"margin-left:0px;\" class=\"edm_outlooklist\"><ul style=\"list-style-type:none;padding:0px 0px 0px 0px;margin:0px 0px;\"><li class=\"listItem ff\" style=\"list-style-type:none;text-align:left;\"><a href=\"https://link.mail.beehiiv.com/v1/c/7IwTCC7SOr%2BRLRQs5uRWpNxZiK74b0azYz6Eqhj0rNe0Z4zthSejkykuzjKp%0ATGlFbIL0TeSBHxtE7OTCLLGME38MPLnfnj3r9uPaP2GmHXxzV0wDkeijAO2k%0A9grR%2BgEo53wkN83EQZ%2BWZOP%2Bdj8htcy7rtVWyMv4EX%2FfTIg5R9gmVh5EmZGY%0AtmwZ19aLvQPF